text: FX is an Dutch pay television channel owned by Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA. The channel originally launched as the Dutch version of Discovery Home & Health on 24 January 2014. On 25 January 2024, Warner Bros. Discovery EMEA announced that the Dutch version of Discovery Home & Health would be rebranded as FX on 6 April 2024. == Logos == file:Discovery H&H.png;|24 January 2014-6 April 2024 file:FX Logo 2023.svg|6 April 2024-present Category:Television channels in Europe
